message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with audio and speech processing. Other likely categories could be cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SI, and cs.MM. cs.LG deals with machine learning, which is the core of the proposed system. cs.CV deals with computer vision, which can be related to the image-like representation of the spectrogram. cs.SI deals with signal processing, which is the core of the proposed system. cs.MM deals with multimedia, which can be related to the music mixture.
